{"tid":1600984,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【胡少江評論】習近平的權力慶典和中華民族的災難記錄","createTime":"2019-09-28T23:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T10:56:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9c2025f801606be27b24ca063067e60e1cd7785f","tid":1600984,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T23:53:10.000Z","msg":"【胡少江評論】習近平的權力慶典和中華民族的災難記錄<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dHGK9feH_B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdHGK9feH_B8&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=0b236a7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dHGK9feH_B8</a><br />\n<br />\nRFA 自由亞洲粵語 <br />\n<br />\nPublished on Sep 28, 2019<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tiny.cc/7yykdz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftiny.cc%2F7yykdz&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=ac5935e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tiny.cc/7yykdz</a><br />\n<br />\n中國共產黨奪取全國政權已經七十年了，目前的北京政權正面臨日益窘迫的內外環境︰國內經濟增速持續下滑；科技發展和出口貿易在美中貿易戰中遭受重創；世界上所有的文明力量正在集體發聲，譴責北京在少數民族地區犯下的侵犯人權的嚴重罪行；香港數百萬人上街反對中央政府移植大陸的極權制度，等等。雖然如此，北京卻正在緊鑼密鼓地為大規模慶祝活動進行超豪華的準備。不難理解，習近平實在是太需要一個顯示自己權力的慶典了，中國實在是太需要一個能夠掩蓋衝天晦氣的、自欺欺人的虛假歡樂氛圍了。<br />\n<br />\n#文化大革命<br />\n#中共建政70周年<br />\n#民族災難<br />\n<br />\n（以上評論純屬作者個人觀點，並不代表本台立場。）<br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台（Radio Free Asia）總部設在美國華盛頓，為言論自由受限的亞洲國家和地區提供完整而免費的新聞報道。致力以多媒體形式發送新聞，成為一個讓大眾獲得可靠消息的平台。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n訂閱自由亞洲電台粵語部頻道 <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/subscription_c...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fsubscription_c...&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=b0a13cef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/subscription_c...</a><br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台粵語部 | RFA Cantonese<br />\n<br />\n網址：<a href=\"http://www.rfa.org/cantonese\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=e16ebc5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfa.org/cantonese</a><br />\nFacebook 臉書：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcantonese.rfa&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=4ed6404d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa</a><br />\nTwitter 推特：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Rfacantonese\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRfacantonese&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=87326c2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Rfacantonese</a><br />\nGoogle +：<a href=\"https://plus.google.com/+CantoneseRFA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplus.google.com%2F%2BCantoneseRFA&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=b6a8480a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://plus.google.com/+CantoneseRFA</a><br />\nYouTube：<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/cantoneseRFA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2FcantoneseRFA&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=b3e33656\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/user/cantoneseRFA</a><br />\nSoundCloud: <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/rfacantonese\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Frfacantonese&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=5eadf108\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/rfacantonese</a>"},{"pid":"fdc07eb699e93f0a74c9554a7fb9eb5f77410fa0","tid":1600984,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:08:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">push</span>"},{"pid":"77406e082bbce7d800c378d94b5a49ca51796994","tid":1600984,"uid":271434,"like":0,"di